      <title>Lenoir city Recycling resources</title>
      <link>https://meidiw.github.io/posts/lenoir_city-recycle/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Aug 2025 22:29:32 -0400</pubDate>
      <guid>https://meidiw.github.io/posts/lenoir_city-recycle/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;搬来小村了（失去了recycling curbside pickup），但也要好好回收！&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;上篇写过的terracyle在本地有几个项目，列在文末。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-回收中心&#34;&gt;1. 回收中心&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;附近一共有&lt;a href=&#34;https://loudoncounty-tn.gov/convenience-centers/&#34;&gt;三个&lt;/a&gt;，最近的是Lenoir City Convenience Center:&lt;br&gt;
500 Halls Ferry Road Lenoir City, TN 37771

&lt;div style=&#34;position:relative; width:50%; padding-bottom:1.25%;&#34;&gt;
   &lt;iframe src=&#34;https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3236.7926852094083!2d-84.28015648776712!3d35.78046857244106!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x885dd557a3afb01f%3A0x2ebabcf92bc34deb!2sLoudon%20County%20Convenience%20Center!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1754445507781!5m2!1sen!2sus&#34; width=&#34;600&#34; height=&#34;450&#34; style=&#34;border:0;&#34; allowfullscreen=&#34;&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; referrerpolicy=&#34;no-referrer-when-downgrade&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;img alt=&#34;what they accept&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://meidiw.github.io/images/lc_acceptlist.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-soft-plastics&#34;&gt;2. soft plastics&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;门口walmart接受各种软塑料
&lt;img alt=&#34;plastics types&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://meidiw.github.io/images/walmart.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;3-local-terracycle-projects&#34;&gt;3. Local terracycle projects&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Knoxfill 通过terracycle有好几个项目
&lt;strong&gt;地址&lt;/strong&gt;：6204 Chapman Hwy, Knoxville, Tennessee 37920
&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.knoxfill.com/specialty-recycling&#34;&gt;接受物品&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;电池&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;个人护理包装（塑料，玻璃，铝，不接受气罐，香水瓶，眼线笔，木质包装）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;口腔用品包装&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;球鞋&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;4-purchase-with-cautious&#34;&gt;4. Purchase with cautious&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;红色小村里回收资源少了很多，更要谨慎购物！！
前面提到的&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.knoxfill.com/&#34;&gt;knoxfill&lt;/a&gt;很好，是一间zero waste商店，各种日用产品（厨房护肤婴儿用品等等等等）都可以自己带容器或者用店里的容器refill！（houston曾经也有一间这样的店，但covid期间倒闭了。。。。）

&lt;div style=&#34;position:relative; width:50%; padding-bottom:1.25%;&#34;&gt;
    &lt;iframe src=&#34;https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3231.031888817972!2d-83.8770295877623!3d35.92171947239599!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x837df4e27e2a4d03%3A0xe57bbe1384115d7c!2sKnoxFill!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1754445375260!5m2!1sen!2sus&#34; width=&#34;600&#34; height=&#34;450&#34; style=&#34;border:0;&#34; allowfullscreen=&#34;&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; referrerpolicy=&#34;no-referrer-when-downgrade&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

小小的独立二手书店：&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.addisonsbooks.com/&#34;&gt;Addison&amp;rsquo;s bookstore&lt;/a&gt;, 地址：

&lt;div style=&#34;position:relative; width:50%; padding-bottom:10.25%;&#34;&gt;
    &lt;iframe src=&#34;https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3274.210276831853!2d-83.9224626298327!3d35.9682348955242!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x885c1734074f5f89%3A0x9de216cba535f901!2sAddison&amp;#39;s%20Bookstore!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1754445469679!5m2!1sen!2sus&#34; width=&#34;600&#34; height=&#34;450&#34; style=&#34;border:0;&#34; allowfullscreen=&#34;&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; referrerpolicy=&#34;no-referrer-when-downgrade&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</description>
